Customer Support


 Mattson is committed to providing our customers
                   with World Class Service and Support through an ongoing partnership
                  
                  with our customers.
                  Mattson continuously strives to provide trained and experienced 
                      resources.
                      All Field Service Engineers are provided with product specific 
                      training and field experience as part of a formalized Field 
                      Service Engineer Certification program. 

Mattson continuously strives to provide on-time demand 
                      parts.
                      24 X 7 parts support is provided for down equipment. 

Mattson continuously strives for regularly scheduled, 
                      open communication forums.
                      Account Managers and Service Managers regularly meet with 
                      our customers to review Mattson's performance. 

                      Mattson will work to achieve the highest possible tool output 
                      through the delivery of uncompromising support and communication. 
                    

For assistance with Field Service, Parts, or Technical Support,
                     please call your local Mattson office or the Mattson response
                    
                    center at 1-800-315-6607 or 1-845-575-6203. 
We can also be reached via email at: 

Field Support Programs: servicemarketing@mattson.com
Parts Support: partssupport@mattson.com
Technical Publications: techpubs@mattson.com
Technical Support 
                      
Thermal Products: thermaltechsupport@mattson.com
Plasma Products: plasmatechsupport@mattson.com


