Company Description


Mattson Technology, Inc. designs, manufactures, markets, and supports semiconductor wafer processing equipment used in the fabrication of integrated circuits (ICs) worldwide. The firm supplies dry strip and rapid thermal processing equipment to the global semiconductor industry. The company was founded by Brad Mattson in 1988 and is headquartered in Fremont, CA.




Website


http://www.mattson.com






