 Suppliers



Ultra Clean Holdings, Inc.

                                     •  Semiconductors                                                                             •  Dover, DE                                                                    

                                    Ultra Clean Holdings, Inc. engages in the development, manufacture, and supply of semiconductor capital equipment. It offers supply chain management, metal fabrication, precision machining, system integration, thermal control, and three-dimensional printing. The company was founded in November 2002 and is headquartered in Hayward, CA.
                                




Canon Marketing Japan, Inc.

                                     •  Wholesale: Consumer Durables                                                                             •  Tokyo, TY                                                                    

                                    Canon Marketing Japan Inc. engages in the distribution of electronic office equipment. It operates through the following segments: Business Solutions, Information Technology (IT) Solutions, Imaging System, and Industrial/Medical. The Business Solutions segment offers business-use multifunctional products, print-on-demand digital presses, personal-use plain paper copiers, laser printers, large format ink-jet printers, office-use facsimiles, liquid crystal projectors, document scanners, color card printers, color label printers, teleconference system, network cameras, and support services. The IT Solutions segment deals with systems integration, embedded software, infrastructure, outsourcing, software products, computer devices, and network equipment. The Imaging System segment handles digital cameras, interchangeable lenses, digital video cameras, ink-jet printers, compact photo printers, personal-use scanners, electronic dictionaries, calculators, and commercial imaging equipment. The Industrial/Medical segment provides semiconductor manufacturing equipment, optical measuring equipment, digital radiography, medical systems, sterilizers, and medicine packing machines. The company was founded in February 1968 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
                                




